The paper deals with communication between information systems, which involves concepts from artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The study of properties and extensions of general relation mappings involves topics related to data structures (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the application of fuzzy information systems relates to soft computing (cs.SI).
